content:
System.Web.Configuration.Internal Namespace

Definition

The System.Web.Configuration.Internal namespace contains configuration types intended for internal use only.

In this Article

Interfaces

IInternalConfigWebHost

Defines interfaces used by internal .NET Framework infrastructure for accessing and manipulating Host configuration files.
